<view class="container">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">个人信息</view>
    
    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label required">输入你的学校</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请输入学校" bindinput="onSchoolInput" value="{{formData.school}}"/>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
      
      <!-- 移动下拉列表到这里 -->
      <view class="school-select" wx:if="{{showSchoolSelect}}">
        <view class="school-item" 
              wx:for="{{schoolList}}" 
              wx:key="index"
              bindtap="onSelectSchool"
              data-school="{{item}}">
          {{item}}
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label required">选择你的院校和专业</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请选择" bindinput="onMajorInput"/>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label required">选择你的学级</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请选择" bindinput="onGradeInput"/>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label required">选择你的当前排名</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请选择" bindinput="onRankInput"/>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label required">输入擅长科目</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请输入" bindinput="onProjectInput"/>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label required">是否一战</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请选择" bindinput="onFirstTryInput"/>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">目标院校</view>
    
    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label">期望学校</text>
      <text class="input">请填写学校全称，多所院校请用逗号开</text>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label">期望专业</text>
      <text class="input">不同专业请用逗号开</text>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label">期望城市</text>
      <text class="input">多城市请用逗号开</text>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <text class="label">学校程度</text>
      <text class="input">请选择</text>
      <image class="arrow" src="/assets/icons/arrow.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tips">
    <view class="tip-item">
      <image class="tip-icon" src="/assets/icons/tip.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
      <text>如果您有明确的期望学院，无明确的期望专业时：填写期望院校，专业/城市/学校程度可选填小范围。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="tip-item">
      <image class="tip-icon" src="/assets/icons/tip.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
      <text>如果您有明确的期望专业，无明确期望学校时：填写期望专业，学校/城市/学校程度可选填小范围。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="tip-item">
      <image class="tip-icon" src="/assets/icons/tip.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
      <text>如果您有明确城市，其他无明确：填写城市即可。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="tip-item">
      <image class="tip-icon" src="/assets/icons/tip.png" mode="aspectFit"/>
      <text>如果您想对比多个不同院校、不同专业：如：上海交通大学计算机系 及 厦门大学会计系，请在目标院校1填写上海交通大学 计算机系专业。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <button class="submit-btn" bindtap="onSubmit">开始查询</button>
</view>